    "Additional material Open data APIThe S3 bucket containing the NeuronBridge matches forms an open REST API.",
    "Key structures are arranged such that they can be queried predictably.",
    "We use the standard JSON format and publish a schema for each document type.",
    "The schemas are versioned so that future changes are not breaking.",
    "All of the endpoints below are relative to the bucket root at s3://janelia-neuronbridge-data-prod • current.txtReturns the current version, to be used in subsequent API calls as <VER>."
